<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>Global clean energy supply chains stand at a critical intersection of integration and decoupling. This research theme studies the benefits, costs, and risks of clean energy global supply chains to inform international and domestic climate policies to enable sustainable, rapid, and just energy transitions to achieve climate goals.</p>
</section>
