  <link>http://deeppolicylab.github.io/research/energy-nexus-research/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<div class="quarto-figure quarto-figure-center">
<figure class="figure">
<p><img src="http://deeppolicylab.github.io/research/energy-nexus-research/featured.png" class="img-fluid figure-img"></p>
<figcaption>Created by Copilot</figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>Understanding how energy nexus systems interact and influence each other within the broader context of resource management, sustainable development, climate change, and human well-being. This nexus approach recognizes that decisions in one domain (e.g., energy production) have cascading effects on others (e.g., water resources, carbon emissions, and social systems).</p>
</section>
<section id="featured-publications" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="featured-publications">Featured publications</h2>
<div id="listing-featured-publications" class="quarto-listing quarto-listing-container-grid">
<div class="list grid quarto-listing-cols-2">
<div class="g-col-1" data-index="0" data-listing-date-sort="1691380800000">
