<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>China is the world’s largest emitter of greenhouse gases. It has set a target to achieve carbon peak by 2030 and carbon neutrality by 2060. This initiative aims to facilitate the transition to a low-carbon economy in China to achieve the national carbon peak and carbon neutrality targets.</p>
