<section id="overview" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="overview">Overview</h2>
<p>The Climate Leadership and Community Protection Act (CLCPA) aims to reduce greenhouse gas emissions to 40% below 1990 levels by 2030 and then to 85% below 1990 levels by 2050. This initiative aims to facilitate the implementation of the CLCPA to achieve the state’s climate goals.</p>
